Name: Sturdy Fishing Pole
Description:
A fishing pole made of stronger materials.
It has higher durability and can slightly increase the speed of reeling in fish after a bite.
The fishing pole has durability, and fishing will consume the rod's durability. Once the durability is exhausted, the rod will be lost.
This type of rod will not accidentally break while fishing.
